{
  "page": "Perfumed Garden",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Perfumed Garden</b> is a famous <a href=\"/index.php/Pleasure_house\" title=\"Pleasure house\">pillow house</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lys</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Perfumed_Garden&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Perfumed Garden was one of the many holdings owned by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Rogare\" title=\"House Rogare\">House Rogare</a> under <a href=\"/index.php/Lysandro_Rogare\" title=\"Lysandro Rogare\">Lysandro \"the Magnificent\"</a>. In <a href=\"/index.php/135_AC\" title=\"135 AC\">135&#160;AC</a>, Lysandro drowned when his opulent barge sank whilst carrying him from the Perfumed Garden back to his palace. \n</p><p>A younger son of Lysandro, <a href=\"/index.php/Fredo_Rogare\" title=\"Fredo Rogare\">Fredo</a>, inherited the Perfumed Garden. When the <a href=\"/index.php/Rogare_Bank\" title=\"Rogare Bank\">Rogare Bank</a> ran dry, Fredo was put on trial, and the Rogare Bank was seized, along with the bed-slaves there. When the Rogare's assets proved insufficient to cover their debts, the Rogares were also sold into slavery, with the daughters of <a href=\"/index.php/Lysaro_Rogare\" title=\"Lysaro Rogare\">Lysaro</a> and Fredo Rogare becoming bed-slaves in the Perfumed Garden.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Perfumed_Garden&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Lysene Spring and the End of Regency.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404060355\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.022 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.045 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 221/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8607/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 818/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 418/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1077/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.51 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   39.825      1 -total\n 78.52%   31.271      1 Template:Date\n 15.59%   